WEBVTT

00:00:01.458 --> 00:00:03.809
A friend called me a few weeks ago

00:00:03.833 --> 00:00:05.768
with bad news.

00:00:05.792 --> 00:00:08.170
She dropped her cell phone
into the toilet.

00:00:09.083 --> 00:00:10.934
Anyone here done that before?

00:00:10.958 --> 00:00:12.643
(Laughter)

00:00:12.667 --> 00:00:14.226
So it was a bad situation.

00:00:14.250 --> 00:00:17.601
You know, without getting into the details
of exactly how that happened

00:00:17.625 --> 00:00:19.518
or how she got it out,

00:00:19.542 --> 00:00:22.018
let's just say it was a bad situation.

00:00:22.042 --> 00:00:24.768
And she panicked because,
like for many of us,

00:00:24.792 --> 00:00:29.226
her phone is one of the most used
and essential tools in her life.

00:00:29.250 --> 00:00:32.268
But, on the other hand,
she had no idea how to fix it,